text: Megalorhipida leptomeres is a moth of the family Pterophoridae. It is known from the Democratic Republic of Congo, Kenya, Tanzania, South Africa, La Réunion, Madagascar, the Seychelles, Oman and Yemen. == References == Category:Oxyptilini Category:Moths described in 1886 Category:Moths of Asia Category:Moths of Africa Category:Moths of Madagascar Category:Moths of the Middle East Category:Moths of Réunion Category:Moths of Seychelles
